race.description: Moruya Mitre 10 Moruya Showcase Town Plate Handicap
race.comment: Strong race with plenty of chances. YOUR NOT THE BOSS (11) attacked the line strongly at his first run back with an unlucky third over 1300m at this track in the Narooma Cup. Goes just as well second-up and he should get the right tempo to take stopping. VELLA FOX (8) held up slightly in the straight and strong through the line when a gritty fourth over 1010m at this track. Proven at the trip and comes here in peak condition. KING TAURUS (13) two of his four wins have come at this track and drops sharply in grade. Closed well when sixth to Axius over this trip at Randwick in BM78 grade. Leading chance with the claim. WHO BUT ROO (3) underrated sprinter holding his form in the city. Has a good record here and just needs luck from the sticky gate. Respect. The chances don't end there.
